              "active": true,
              "timeZone": "Europe/London"
            },
            "body": "we do have log issues in long-lived apps, but different ones, YARN-1104 and YARN-1111 look at those.\n\nfor those services we don't want the logs aggregated at the end of the run, more streamed off while the app runs along. I don't know if this plugin mechanism would help at that phase, unless the logs were being snapshotted and rolled out.\n",
